name: Pure
description: Pure reflects my inner journey; specifically, the experiences that made me into a survivor, artist, and poet. The victory that the poem and art piece reflect is a rebirth of softness. The figure’s eyes are wide, as are mine, open to the odyssey of new encounters that each new day presents. Pure is featured in iDENTITY | 01 | BIT.SHES Summer 2021 Collection. All proceeds from this piece go to charity. Check out bitshes.com for more info!
